== A Talmudist? ==

I know of know actual evidence that Ralbag was a talmudist and will be removing this claim from the opening paragraph until it can be substantiated. I know that later authorities claimed him to be a Talmudist, but this has little support (and is likely out of a desire that popular parshanim also be famous in the talmud world, which Rashi was, but Ibn Ezra, Ralbag, etc, were not). [[user:jnothman|jnothman]] [[User_talk:jnothman|<sup>talk</sup>]] 00:55, 26 October 2007 (UTC)

